name: PlemCo Ship N-Crc079
description:
Very nimble shunting tug

PlemCo SpaceShip is a project about drawing spaceships using increasing quantity of blocks. Every ship is unique and more complex than previous one.
Every 10 items I get a new word to picture with my SpaceShips.

First 70 Ships were Frozen in Polygon at OpenSea: https://opensea.io/collection/plemcospaceships
